**Time, a concept for odd people**

As always, if you want something to change in this discord say so and get a few people to support you. If supported it will be done.

**Straight from the mind without spellcheck**
So yeah, crazy year hasn’t it been. We lost a few people to life, another few people are pushing life to their bounds and some are still here playing games. Wonderful isn’t it. If you compare how this discord looked a year ago it was completely different. Yes, maybe it was more fun, more interactions and that. But it was not a state most of us could have continued in. Personally I am very happy to see the people who are and aren’t here making the choices that they are. Some quick personal advice, stop being stuck in the past. Try to make the now as fun as you considered the past to be.
